<h1 id="nested-blocks">Nested blocks</h1>
<p>Variables defined using <code>let</code> and <code>const</code> are available only inside <code>{...}</code> blocks, and other blocks inside them.</p>
<pre><code class="language-js">function run (user) {
  if (user) {
    let running = user.state === 'running'
    if (running) {
      /*[ `running` is still available here ]*/
    } else {
      /*[ and here, too ]*/
    }
  } else {
    /*[ but not here! ]*/
  }
}
</code></pre>
